parameters:
Passerby: "Aaaaah, a naked hunk is strutting around in front
of the station! And he's... huge...!"

Passerby: "Is this some kind of shoot for women's porn...?
Even as a guy, I can't help but admire that body..."

Anomalocaris: "D-damn it, don't look... Don't you look at
me...! Me... Anomalocaris, to suffer such humiliation...!!"

Anomalocaris was born as the second son of a karate dojo,
winning trophies in numerous competitions, yet failed in his
job search and became a monster... Now, stripped of all his
pride and dignity, he trembles in his birth-given form...

Anomalocaris: "Huff huff... If I defecate here, I can earn
the right to a rematch...! Then I can defeat that little
girl and return to the top of the organization...!! I'll do
it...!! Uoooooh...!!!"

Bunny-chan: "He's passed out... The challenge is a
failure... There will be no rematch!! Please withdraw...
Men! Someone take him away-!"

Memimi: "Anomalocaris... You didn't get your rematch, but I
fully acknowledge your resolve... I won't let anyone laugh
at you... Yeah..."

Although Anomalocaris couldn't escape his position as a low-
ranking member of the organization, his female fanbase in
the city grew rapidly, and even the members of the
organization began to respect him...
